{
    "679:0": "atha pañcacatvāriṃśaḥ paṭalavisaraḥ |",
    "679:1": "athakhalu bhagavāṃ śākyamuniḥ punarapi mañjuśriyaṃ kumārabhūtamāmantrayate sma |",
    "679:2": "sarvāṃ ca śuddhāvāsabhavanasannipatitāṃ devagaṇānāmantrayate sma |",
    "679:3": "śṛṇvantu bhavanto devasaṅghāḥ ! mañjuśriyasya kumārabhūtasya mahāṛddhivikurvaṇaprātihāryavikrīḍitaceṣṭitabālarūpasvarūpanidarśanayathāśayatvasantoṣaṇamahāyānāgradharmaprāpaṇaṃ sattvapākasaṃyojanamudrāmantraprabhāvatatrasattvayojanamabhiprāyasampūraṇārthaṃ mudrāpaṭalaṃ paramaguhyatamaṃ sarvamantratantrakalpeṣu bījabhūtaṃ sārabhūtaṃ paramarahasyaṃ mahāguhyatamaṃ paramottaratantreṣu sarvalaukikalokottareṣu aprakāśyaṃ paramagopyaṃ nāśiṣyāṇāṃ ca deyam aśrāddhānāmanutpāditabodhicittānāṃ matsariṇāmanyatīrthāyatanabhaktyānāṃ mahāyānāgradharmavidveṣiṇāṃ sarvamantratantreṣu agauravajātānām |",
    "679:4": "eteṣāṃ prakāśya anyeṣāṃ prakāśyamiti samayajñānāṃ buddhaśāsane pratipannānāṃ surūpasuveṣaśrāddhamavikalacittasandhānamahotsāhā sarvamantreṣu ca sagaurava sarvabuddhabodhisattveṣu pratyekabuddhāryaśrāvaka sarvadeva sabrahmacārī sapratīsādarajāteṣu sattveṣu mahāsannāhasannaddheṣu sakalasattvādhātvottāraṇābhyudyamodyateṣu mahākāruṇikeṣu kṣāntisaurabhyasuvacaskeṣu sattveṣveteṣāṃ deyamanyeṣāmadeyamityāhu ca ||",
    "679:5": "eka mudrāgaṇaḥ śreṣṭhaḥ prayukto mantrayojitaḥ |",
    "679:6": "karoti karma vividhā maneṣṭā manuyojitā ||",
    "679:7": "jāpibhiḥ sarvakālaṃ tu prayoktavyaḥ siddhimicchatā |",
    "679:8": "nāmnā trailokyavikhyātaḥ buddhaiḥ ajitaḥ sadā ||",
    "679:9": "strīsampatkaro hyeṣa prathitaḥ sarvajantubhiḥ |",
    "679:10": "śrīvatso nāma mudro'yaṃ pramukho'ṣṭaśate bhuvi ||",
    "679:11": "mudrāṇāmaṣṭaśataṃ jñeyaṃ mañjughoṣa ! śṛṇohi me |",
    "679:12": "purā jinavarairgītaṃ buddhaputraiśca dhāritam ||",
    "679:13": "ahaṃ vakṣye pratyahaṃ varttamānamanāgatam |",
    "679:14": "arthārthaṃ samanumodye rakṣye'haṃ bhuvanatraye ||",
    "679:15": "mañjughoṣastathā hṛṣṭaḥ uvāca vadatāṃ varam|",
    "679:16": "deśayantu mahātmāno buddhāḥ sarvatra pūjitāḥ ||",
    "679:17": "yaṃ śrutvā puruṣāḥ prājñāḥ niyataṃ bodhimāśraye |",
    "679:18": "sarveṣāṃ tu pravṛttānāṃ japahomavrate sthitām ||",
    "679:19": "dhruvaṃ mantrāstu siddhyeyurimairmudraistu mudritāḥ |",
    "679:20": "adhyeṣye'haṃ mahāvīraṃ śākyasiṃhaṃ narottamam ||",
    "679:21": "asmākaṃ sattvamarthāya dharmakośārthapūraṇam |",
    "679:22": "mahāyānāgradharmārthaṃ mantracaryārthasādhaka ||",
    "679:23": "durdāntadamakaṃ puṇyaṃ pavitraṃ pāpanāśanam |",
    "679:24": "deśayantu mahāvīrā paṭalaṃ mudrasambhavam ||",
    "679:25": "pūraṇārthaṃ tu mudrāṇāṃ sūcanārthaṃ tu devatām |",
    "679:26": "anukampārthaṃ tu jāpinām ||",
    "679:27": "evamuktvā tu mañjuśrīḥ kumāro bālarūpiṇaḥ |",
    "679:28": "nirīkṣya sugataśreṣṭhaṃ sukho mañjuravastadā ||",
    "679:29": "uvāca madhurāṃ vāṇīṃ muniśreṣṭho vināyaka |",
    "679:30": "kalaviṅkarutaḥ śrīmāṃ meghadundubhiniḥsvanaḥ ||",
    "679:31": "brahmasvareṇa vacasā vāco mabhyācacakṣa saḥ |",
    "679:32": "śṛṇotha bhūtagaṇāḥ sarve kalpārthaṃ mantradevatām ||",
    "679:33": "samayaṃ sarvadaivānāṃ mukhyaṃ mudrāśca daivatam |",
    "679:34": "samatikrāntabuddhaistu pratyekārhatasādhakaiḥ ||",
    "679:35": "kaḥ punaranyasattvaistu vidyādaivatalaukikaiḥ |",
    "679:36": "eṣa mudrāgaṇajyeṣṭhaḥ sarvamudreṣu katthyate ||",
    "679:37": "yaṃ tathā jāpinaḥ sarve niyataṃ siddhyanti devatā |",
    "679:38": "ādau kisalayaṃ nāmnā dvitīyaṃ bhavati mekhalā ||",
    "679:39": "tṛtīyaṃ sumekhalā caiva caturthī sumanusodbhavā |",
    "679:40": "pañcamī saṅkaletyāhuḥ ṣaṣṭhī rekhā praghuṣyate ||",
    "679:41": "suvarṇā saptamī jñeyā mālā bhavati cāṣṭamī |",
    "679:42": "navamī aṅkuśī khyātā daśamī saptadaśacchadā ||",
    "679:43": "ekādaśī bhavet kuntā sukuntā dvādaśī bhavet |",
    "679:44": "kardamī trayodaśī cātra paṭahī pañcadaśī bhavet ||",
    "679:45": "ṣoḍaśī tu bhaved yaṣṭiḥ muṣṭiḥ saptadaśī viduḥ |",
    "679:46": "aṣṭādaśa samākhyātā vajramālā pragīyate ||",
    "679:47": "hemamālonaviṃśā tu padmamālā tha viṃśati |",
    "679:48": "nāgī nāgamukhī caiva tṛtīyā bhavati mahāmukhī ||",
    "679:49": "vaktrā ca vaktrasahitā chatrī bhavati lohitā |",
    "679:50": "lohitā cāṣṭaviṃśā tu nīlalohitikā sinī ||",
    "679:51": "jyotsnā jani tāmasī dvātriṃśā kathitā bhuvi |",
    "679:52": "tārā sutārā tārāvartā sumudrajāpi ||",
    "679:53": "ghorarūpiṇī vikhyātā rātrī bhayadā sadā |",
    "679:54": "mahāprabhāveti vikhyātā yā mudrā bhuvi locanā ||",
    "679:55": "saptatriṃśatimudrāstu saṅkhyā hyeṣā pragīyate |",
    "679:56": "śvetā paṇḍarā caiva evalā māmakī ca yā ||",
    "679:57": "mahābhayaharī devī bhrukuṭī tu pragīyate |",
    "679:58": "ajitā aparājitā khyātā jayā vijayā parājitā ||",
    "679:59": "sādhakī sādhanī caiva tārā śveteti gīyate |",
    "679:60": "ghaṭakarparamityāhuḥ sugatī gatiśodhikā ||",
    "679:61": "padmī padmasutā caiva vajrī vajramanodbhavā |",
    "679:62": "strīsaṅkhyā gaṇo mudraiḥ puruṣāṇāṃ tu pragīyate ||",
    "679:63": "bhadraṃ mudrapīṭhaṃ tu āsanaṃ śayanaṃ bhuvi |",
    "679:64": "svayambhūśambhucakraśca kuliśo musalastathā ||",
    "679:65": "svastiko liṅgamudraśca pakṣirāḍ garutmanaḥ |",
    "679:66": "mudro garuḍadhvajo jñeyaḥ viṣṇurudrasavāsavaḥ ||",
    "679:67": "brahmā padmodbhavaḥ śrīmāṃ śrīsampuṭa eva ca |",
    "679:68": "tathyaṃ yamalamudraṃ ca mayūrāsanameva tu ||",
    "679:69": "viditaṃ sarvadig dhīmāṃ kārttikeyārthadaḥ sadā |",
    "679:70": "kumārasyānucaro jñeyaḥ mañjughoṣasya ||",
    "679:71": "tasya mudraṃ mahāvīryaṃ tā tāḥ śaktidharaḥ sadā |",
    "679:72": "mayūrāsanamudraṃ tu tasyaivaitat prayujyate ||",
    "679:73": "anena baddhvā mantreṇa kārttikeyasya yuktitaḥ |",
    "679:74": "yāvanto laukikā mudrā śaivāścaiva savāsavāḥ ||",
    "679:75": "sarve bhavanti baddhvā vai vaśyārthaṃ hi prayujyate |",
    "679:76": "eṣa mudrā karo hyarthāṃ puṣkalāṃ sādhu ceṣṭitām ||",
    "679:77": "prasanno buddhaputrasya mañjughoṣasya dhīmataḥ |",
    "679:78": "buddhaśāsanamavatīrṇo bālarūpī maharddhikaḥ ||",
    "679:79": "kārttikeyo'tha vikhyātaḥ mantramukhye'tha laukike |",
    "679:80": "sarveṣāṃ ca prayoktavyo bāliśānāṃ viśeṣataḥ ||",
    "679:81": "grahamātarakūṣmāṇḍaiḥ gṛhītā kaṭapūtanaiḥ |",
    "679:82": "daityadānavayakṣaiśca piśācoragarākṣasaiḥ ||",
    "679:83": "kravyādairmānuṣaiścāpi nityaṃ cāpi vimokṣakaḥ |",
    "679:84": "raudrasattve'tha duṣṭebhiḥ piśitāśanavyantaraiḥ ||",
    "679:85": "mudritebhiśca manujairmudro'yaṃ sampramokṣakaḥ |",
    "679:86": "sarvasattvārthayuktaśca prayuktaḥ sukhadaḥ sadā ||",
    "679:87": "saṃkṣepeṇa tu ukto'yaṃ vistaraścaiva saṃjñakam |",
    "679:88": "aparaṃ mudraṃ pravakṣyāmi yaṃ baddhvā sukhī bhavet ||",
    "679:89": "jāpinaḥ sarvakarmeṣu prayuktasyāpyamoghavām |",
    "679:90": "nāmnā buddhāsano nāma mahāmudrā prakatthyate ||",
    "679:91": "vistaraḥ sarvatantreṣu paṭhyate tāṃ nibodhata |",
    "679:92": "yaṃ baddhvā jāpinaḥ sarve niyataṃ bodhiparāyaṇāḥ ||",
    "679:93": "kaḥ punaḥ siddhikāmānāṃ bhogālipsaparāyaṇam |",
    "679:94": "pūrvava caukṣasamācāraḥ sthitvā ca prāṅmukhaḥ śuciḥ ||",
    "679:95": "ubhau hastau samau kṛtvā añjalyākāramāśṛtau |",
    "679:96": "kuryād vikāsitau cāgre ubhāvaṅguṣṭhanāmitau ||",
    "679:97": "madhyamāṅgulimāśliṣṭau kuṇḍalākāracihnitau |",
    "679:98": "paryaṅkenopaviṣṭe tu nābhideśe tadā nyaset ||",
    "679:99": "eṣa mudrāvaraḥ śreṣṭhaḥ sarvakarmeṣu yojitaḥ |",
    "679:100": "uttameṣu ca uttiṣṭhe nādhame madhyame'pi vā ||",
    "679:101": "kṣipramarthakaro hyeṣa siddhaḥ sarvatra yujyate |",
    "679:102": "mahāpuṇyo pavitro'yaṃ maṅgalyamaghanāśanaḥ ||",
    "679:103": "sarvapāpaharaḥ puṇyaḥ mudro'yaṃ siddhihetavaḥ |",
    "679:104": "dvitīyamaparaṃ mudrā mahāmudrā prakatthyate ||",
    "679:105": "nāmnā śatruñjayī nāma sarvavighnavināśinī |",
    "679:106": "yaṃ baddhvā śatravaḥ sarvāṃ vaśaṃ kuryānna saṃśayaḥ ||",
    "679:107": "sarvecchoṣamāyānti gacchante vātha dāsatām |",
    "679:108": "rāgo dveṣaśca mohaśca svapakṣaḥ sagaṇaiḥ saha ||",
    "679:109": "lokamātsaryamānaśca vicikitsā kathaṃkathā |",
    "679:110": "pramādyo māyā kausīdyaṃ sādhyeṣyā kumārgatā ||",
    "679:111": "mitthyādṛṣṭidaśe māne dante stambhe ca lubdhatā |",
    "679:112": "daśā kuśalapathā karmā sarve te śatravaḥ smṛtāḥ ||",
    "679:113": "eṣa śatrugaṇaḥ prokto buddhairbuddhasu taistathā |",
    "679:114": "eṣa mārgeṣvavasthābhiḥ prāṇino ya ca māśṛtā ||",
    "679:115": "buddhaśāsanahantāraḥ teṣāṃ mudrā prayujyate |",
    "679:116": "iyaṃ mudrā mahāmudrā gītaṃ buddhaiḥ purā sadā |",
    "679:117": "prayoktavyā prāṇināṃ hyeṣā damanārtthaṃ pāpanāśanī |",
    "679:118": "tathaiva purataḥ sthitvā ubhau pāṇisamāśraye ||",
    "679:119": "samāśliṣṭau tha tau kṛtvā añjalyākāramāśṛtau |",
    "679:120": "aṅguṣṭhayugale kṣipraṃ tarjanyau saṃnyasedubhau ||",
    "679:121": "kuṇḍalākārasaṃśliṣṭau tṛtīye parvamāśrayet |",
    "679:122": "eṣā arthakarī mudrā dvitīyā kathitā jinaiḥ ||",
    "679:123": "śatrūṇāṃ nāśayet kṣipraṃ hṛdayāṃsi pradoṣiṇām |",
    "679:124": "tṛtīyaṃ mudraṃ pravakṣyāmi mañjughoṣa ! śṛṇohi tām ||",
    "679:125": "nāmnā śalyaharī divyā sarvaśalyavināśinī |",
    "679:126": "sarvatra yojitā mudrā sarvavyādhicikitsakī ||",
    "679:127": "viṣaśastrakṛtāṃ doṣāṃ jalapāvakasambhavām |",
    "679:128": "anilodbhavadoṣāṃśca duṣṭasattvagarapradām ||",
    "679:129": "kravyādāṃ mānuṣāṃścāpi saviṣāṃ sthāvarajaṅgayām |",
    "679:130": "yacca dehagatāṃ śalyāṃ nārīṇāṃ prasavātminām ||",
    "679:131": "saṃsārābhiratāṃ cānyāṃ prāṇināṃ doṣapīḍitām |",
    "679:132": "sarvanetāstathā śalyāḥ viśalyakaraṇī hyayam ||",
    "679:133": "eṣa mudrā mahāmudrā smaritā sarvajantubhiḥ |",
    "679:134": "viśalyā sukhitā kṣipraṃ bhavate nātra saṃśayaḥ ||",
    "679:135": "nāmamātreṇa te martyā mantrasyāsya prabhāvataḥ |",
    "679:136": "sarvavyādhivinirmuktā vicarante mahītale ||",
    "679:137": "pūrvavaccaukṣasamācārā śucirvastraśucī tadā |",
    "679:138": "badhnīyānmudravaraṃ śreṣṭhaṃ tṛtīyaṃ pāpanāśanam ||",
    "679:139": "ubhau hastau samāyojya viparītākārasambhavām |",
    "679:140": "samau vyaktau añjalyākārau hṛdayasthāne tu taṃ nyaset ||",
    "679:141": "eṣa mudrā mahāmudrā sarvānartthanivāraṇī |",
    "679:142": "yaṃ baddhvā jāpinaḥ sarve niyataṃ bodhiparāyaṇāḥ ||",
    "679:143": "caturthī tu mahāmudrāṃ mahāyakṣīṃ tamādiśet |",
    "679:144": "mahāprabhāvā vijñeyā sarvamantreṣu jāpinām ||",
    "679:145": "atra yakṣagaṇāḥ sarve yakṣiṇyaśca maharddhikāḥ |",
    "679:146": "mantradevatasarveṣu uttamādhamamadhyamāḥ ||",
    "679:147": "sarvasattvaistu sampūjyā mudreyaṃ sampragīyate |",
    "679:148": "ādau baddhvā japenmantraṃ homasādhanakarmasu ||",
    "679:149": "sarvatra yojitā puṇyā sarvamantrāṇi sādhayet |",
    "679:150": "vajrapāṇistathā māntraḥ sarvamudreśvarī hyayam ||",
    "679:151": "paṭhitā lokanāthaistu purā jyeṣṭhairhyatītakaiḥ |",
    "679:152": "tathaiva śucino bhūtvā sthitvā udaṅmukhastadā ||",
    "679:153": "badhnīyānmudravare śreṣṭheḥ sarvakarmeṣu jāpinaḥ |",
    "679:154": "damanārthaṃ sarvabhūtānām ||",
    "679:155": "yathāyaṃ kurute kṣipraṃ yaḥ sattvāceṣṭitaṃ bhuvi |",
    "679:156": "ubhau hastau tadā nyasya sampuṭākāraveṣṭitau ||",
    "679:157": "kuryāt trisūcikākāraṃ aṅguṣṭhau kanyasamadhyamau |",
    "679:158": "anyonyasaṃśliṣṭau caturbhiścāpyatha nāmitau ||",
    "679:159": "kuryānmudravaraṃ hyuktaṃ śiraḥsthāne tu saṃsthitam |",
    "679:160": "yaṃ dṛṣṭvā sarvabhūtā vai vidravanti na saṃśayaḥ ||",
    "679:161": "pañcamī tu mahāmudrā śṛṇu tvaṃ mañjuravaḥ sadā |",
    "679:162": "nāmnā trisamayā caiva mahāpuṇyatamā śivā ||",
    "679:163": "durdāntadamanī nityaṃ sarvasattvārtthasādhanī |",
    "679:164": "ghorarūpī maheśākṣā kālarātrisamaprabhā ||",
    "679:165": "kṛtāntarūpiṇī bhīmā yamasyāpi bhayānikā |",
    "679:166": "caṇḍā ca caṇḍarūpīti duḥprekṣā duḥsahā sadā ||",
    "679:167": "rudravāsavayakṣeṣāṃ rākṣasagrahamātarām |",
    "679:168": "devānanusarāṃścaiva mantramukhyāṃ maharddhikām ||",
    "679:169": "sarvasattvā tathā nityaṃ durdāntadamakī hitā |",
    "679:170": "akālamṛtyuvināśāya mṛtyunāśāya vai hitā ||",
    "679:171": "sṛṣṭā sarvabuddhaistu kṛtāntasyāpi bhayāvahā |",
    "679:172": "yaṃ baddhvā puruṣā nityaṃ samayajñā bhavanti ha ||",
    "679:173": "ye ca mantrāśritā nityaṃ te'pi muktā jape ratā |",
    "679:174": "teṣāṃ siddhyanti mantrā vai ayatnenaiva dehinām ||",
    "679:175": "ajāpino'pi bhavejjāpī aśuciḥ śucino bhavet |",
    "679:176": "saṃyuktaḥ krodharājena yamānteneha mudrayā |",
    "679:177": "sarvakarmakarā hyeṣā saṃyuktā tattvadarśibhiḥ |",
    "679:178": "sarvavighnavināśārthaṃ sarvavyādhicikitsanā ||",
    "679:179": "sarvasattvārthasambhārā sarvaduṣṭanivāraṇā |",
    "679:180": "sarvāsāṃ pūraṇārthāya vihitā munivaraiḥ purā ||",
    "679:181": "eṣa mudrā hitā loke samayabhraṃśācca pūraṇī |",
    "679:182": "baddhvā tu mudravaraṃ śreṣṭhaṃ samayajñastatkṣaṇād bhaved ||",
    "679:183": "sarveṣāṃ caiva mantrāṇāṃ laukikānāṃ ca tatottamāt |",
    "679:184": "praviṣṭo maṇḍalo jñeyaḥ mudrā mantreṇa īritaḥ ||",
    "679:185": "tathaiva śucino bhūtvā pūrvavat sarvakarmasu |",
    "679:186": "trisūcyākāra tathā vajraṃ aṅgulībhiḥ samācaret ||",
    "679:187": "jyeṣṭhamadhyamaaṅgulyau aṅguṣṭhaiśca satā nyaset |",
    "679:188": "mūrdhni sthāne tataḥ kṛtvā apasavyena bhrāmayet ||",
    "679:189": "eṣa mudravarā śreṣṭhā prayuktaḥ sarvakarmasu |",
    "679:190": "etā pañca mahāmudrā lokanāthaistu bhāṣitā ||",
    "679:191": "niyataṃ puruṣavarā baddhvā sambodhyagraṃ spṛśanti ha |",
    "679:192": "sarvāsāṃ pūrayatyete jāpināṃ manasodbhavām ||",
    "679:193": "sarvatathyaṃ yathābhūtaṃ darśayanti yathepsitam |",
    "679:194": "apare mudravarā śreṣṭhā pañca caiva prakāśitā ||",
    "679:195": "śiraḥ vaktro'tha gātraṃ ca utpalaṃ kavacaṃ tathā |",
    "679:196": "ete mudravarā divyā mañjughoṣasya dhīmataḥ ||",
    "679:197": "purā lokavarairmukhyaiḥ kathitā tattvadarśibhiḥ |",
    "679:198": "ahaṃ ca mañjuravaṃ vakṣye katthyamānaṃ nibodhyatām ||",
    "679:199": "śṛṇuṣvaikamanā nityaṃ mudrā mudravarottamām |",
    "679:200": "pūrvavaccaukṣasamācāraḥ sthitvā dhātuvarāgrataḥ ||",
    "679:201": "badhnīyāt karapuṭe nityaṃ mudrāṃ pañcārthasaṃjñikām |",
    "679:202": "ubhe karapuṭāgre tu kuḍmalākārakārite ||",
    "679:203": "dadyuḥ śiravare nityaṃ śiramudreti saṃjñitam |",
    "679:204": "yathaivotpalamudrā tu nyastaḥ duravare sadā ||",
    "679:205": "sā ca sarvataḥ kṣiptā gātramudrā vidhīyate |",
    "679:206": "sa caiva kuto jñeyā vaktramudrā tu sā bhavet ||",
    "679:207": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasya nābhisthāne tu saṃnyaset |",
    "679:208": "īṣi tarjanyāṅgulyanābhimātmanaḥ saṃspṛśet ||",
    "679:209": "sā bhavet kavacamudrā tu ātmarakṣā tu sā bhavet |",
    "679:210": "sarvatra yojitā hyete saphalā sarvārthasādhikā ||",
    "679:211": "ete mudrā mahāmudrā maṅgalyā maghanāśanā |",
    "679:212": "jāpibhiḥ sarvakālaṃ tu prayoktavyāḥ saphalā hitāḥ ||",
    "679:213": "mahāvīryā mahāpuṇyā sarvānarthanivārikā |",
    "679:214": "yaṃ baddhvā puruṣā nityaṃ niyataṃ bodhiparāyaṇāḥ ||",
    "679:215": "apare pañca mahāmudrā lokanāthasya tāpinaḥ |",
    "679:216": "munine śākyasiṃhāya tathā ratnaśikhe gurau ||",
    "679:217": "supuṣpāya sukeśāya tathā sumanasorave |",
    "679:218": "saṅkusumāya ca buddhāya tathā padmottare vare ||",
    "679:219": "sampūrṇāya sunetrāya śuddhā caiva jagadguroḥ |",
    "679:220": "pitāmahāya caiva muktāya jagadvarāmbaramuktaye ||",
    "679:221": "eteṣānāṃ ca buddhānāmanyeṣāṃ ca mahātmanām |",
    "679:222": "atītānāgatā sattvāṃ vartamānāṃ svayambhuvām ||",
    "679:223": "sarveṣānāṃ ca buddhānāṃ mūrdhni sambhūtilakṣaṇā |",
    "679:224": "mahāprabhāvā mahāmudrā samantājjvālamālinaḥ ||",
    "679:225": "uṣṇīṣā iti vikhyātā tṛdhātusamālaye |",
    "679:226": "cakravarttī mahāpuṇyo maṅgalyo maghanāśanā ||",
    "679:227": "sarveṣāṃ ca vidyānāṃ vidyārājaḥ smṛtaḥ prabhuḥ |",
    "679:228": "ekākṣarasaṃyuktaḥ mantro sugatamūrdhajaḥ ||",
    "679:229": "mudro tasya vido jñeyo prabhurekākṣarasya tu |",
    "679:230": "cakravarttī jinakule jāta mudraḥ parameśvaraḥ ||",
    "679:231": "ubhau hastau samāśliṣya sampuṭākāracihnitau |",
    "679:232": "muṣṭiyogena baddhvā vai madhyāṅgulyau susūcitau ||",
    "679:233": "īṣit saṅkocyavatkṛtvā kuṇḍalākāradarśitau |",
    "679:234": "eṣa sarvatrage mudrā sarvamantreśvaro vido ||",
    "679:235": "mūrdhānaṃ devataṃ kṛtvā suṣirākārakuḍmalam |",
    "679:236": "īṣinnāmitatarjanyau kanyasaṃ tu supūjitau ||",
    "679:237": "eṣa mudravaraḥ śreṣṭhaḥ tejorāśe tu kathyate |",
    "679:238": "tadeva sampuṭaṃ cāgryā chatrākārasaṃjñakam ||",
    "679:239": "vikāsyāṅgulī sarvāṃ sitātapatreti saṃjñitam |",
    "679:240": "jayoṣṇīṣaṃ hitaṃ devaṃ hi madhyāṅgulyau susūcitau ||",
    "679:241": "tadeva visāritau cāgre pāṇibhiḥ sarvato gataiḥ |",
    "679:242": "uṣṇīṣasaṅkabhavā jñeyā sarvatrārthadarśibhiḥ ||",
    "679:243": "munimūrdhajasambhūtā mudrā agrā pragīyate |",
    "679:244": "pañcamā tu bhavet sā tu sarvamuṣṇīṣasambhavā ||",
    "679:245": "anena vai sarvabuddhānāṃ yāvantamuṣṇīṣamūrdhajām |",
    "679:246": "sarve te ca samāyānti sarvakarmeṣu yojitā ||",
    "679:247": "sarve munivarairmudrā ye gītā bhuvanatraye |",
    "679:248": "sarveṣāṃ tu mudrāṇāṃ mudreyaṃ parameśvarī ||",
    "679:249": "anenābāhayenmantrāṃ anenaiva visarjayet |",
    "679:250": "anena sarvakarmāṇi kuryāt sarvatra jāpinaḥ ||",
    "679:251": "ete pañca mahāmudrā purā gītā munivaraiḥ |",
    "679:252": "sarvakamārthayuktā vai sarvamuṣṇīṣasādhikā ||",
    "679:253": "yāvanto munivaraiḥ gītā uṣṇīṣā bhuvanatraye |",
    "679:254": "sarveṣāṃ tu sarvatra ime pañcārthapūraṇā ||",
    "679:255": "sarvamuṣṇīṣato jñeyā mudrā vai ca asaṅkhyakā |",
    "679:256": "teṣāṃ pañca varā proktā sarvamuṣṇīṣasādhanī ||",
    "679:257": "avalokitamudrasya pañca vaite sumudrakāḥ |",
    "679:258": "prakṛṣṭā padmakule śreṣṭhā mudre te bhuvi maṇḍale ||",
    "679:259": "uṣṇīṣaṃ ca śirovaktrapadmamudrā ca kathyate |",
    "679:260": "mahākaruṇajā devī tārā bhavati pañcamī ||",
    "679:261": "pūrva caukṣasamācāraḥ dhautavastra sujaptadhīḥ |",
    "679:262": "pāṇinā śirasā mṛśya ūrdhvahasto bhavennaraḥ ||",
    "679:263": "vāmapāṇitale lekhyāṃ muṣṭiyogena veṣṭayet |",
    "679:264": "eṣa uṣṇīṣamudro'yaṃ avalokitamūrdhajām ||",
    "679:265": "tadeva śiravare dattvā śiramudrā pragīyate |",
    "679:266": "tadeva saṅkucitau cāpi nābhideśe pratiṣṭhitau ||",
    "679:267": "vikāsya aṅgulī sarvāṃ padmamudreti sā vidoḥ |",
    "679:268": "upariṣṭādeva vaktrānte hastau tau na samāśṛte ||",
    "679:269": "anyonyamiśritau hastau viralāṅgulimāśritau |",
    "679:270": "tadeva vaktramudrā tu padmaketo'tha gīyate ||",
    "679:271": "yā tu padmadhvaje mudrā nāgaloke prakathyate |",
    "679:272": "sa bhavenmuṣṭiyogena ubhau hastau samāśritau ||",
    "679:273": "ubhau tarjanyatāṃ cordhvau sūcībhūtau sucihnitau |",
    "679:274": "aṅguṣṭhapīḍitau śreṣṭhau tārāmudreti kathyate ||",
    "679:275": "eṣā mudravarā śreṣṭhā karuṇā padmadhvaje vidoḥ |",
    "679:276": "ityevaṃ pañca mahāmudrā kathitā padmālaye sadā ||",
    "679:277": "bodhisattvasya mukhye tā lokeśasya mahātmane |",
    "679:278": "atra padmakule bhavanti bandhaṃ sarvakarmasu ||",
    "679:279": "mantranātheśvaro ye ca vidyā devatalaukikā |",
    "679:280": "sarve te atra vai mudre mudrā yānti sumudritā ||",
    "679:281": "ye ca yakṣeśvarā gītā vajrapāṇimaharddhikā |",
    "679:282": "mahāmantrārttharaudrāśca krodhaprāṇaharā tathā ||",
    "679:283": "ye cānye laukikā mukhyā mantrayuktāśca devatā |",
    "679:284": "sarve te ca samāyānti mudrairetaiḥ sumudritā ||",
    "679:285": "ete mudrā mahāmudrā pavitrā pāpanāśanā |",
    "679:286": "yaṃ baddhvā jāpinaḥ sarve kṣipramāyānti kṣiprataḥ ||",
    "679:287": "muktā tāthāgatī mudrā anyeṣāṃ parameśvarī |",
    "679:288": "avalokitanāthasya sarvavyādhicikitsane ||",
    "679:289": "mudrai to pañca mahābhogā vicaranti mahītale |",
    "679:290": "strīrūpadhāriṇo bhūtvā sarvasattvārthayojitā ||",
    "679:291": "yaṃ baddhvā puruṣā prājña ! niyataṃ bodhiparāyaṇā |",
    "679:292": "aparā pañca mahāmudrā vajrapāṇi maharddhikā ||",
    "679:293": "ya eṣa vajreśvaraḥ śrīmāṃ sarvamantreśvaraḥ prabhuḥ |",
    "679:294": "daśabhūmyapatiḥ śrīmāṃ sarvānarthanivārakaḥ ||",
    "679:295": "mahābhayaprado caṇḍaḥ duṣṭasattvanivāraṇaḥ |",
    "679:296": "dardāntadamako dhīmāṃ dakṣaḥ sattvārthasiddhiṣu ||",
    "679:297": "yakṣarūpeṇa sattvānāṃ ātmanā ceṣṭine bhuvi |",
    "679:298": "sattvārthakriyāyuktaḥ dharmārthamavatārayet ||",
    "679:299": "bodhisambhāramarthāya viceruryakṣarūpiṇaḥ |",
    "679:300": "ye te sattvā hitā loke yakṣiṇyā saha mohitā ||",
    "679:301": "teṣāṃ siddhirna bhavenmantrāṃ vācā duścariteritām |",
    "679:302": "bodhisattvo mahāpuṇyaḥ bahurūpī maharddhikaḥ ||",
    "679:303": "pradoṣya cittaṃ mantreśe kutaḥ siddhyanti mānavāḥ |",
    "679:304": "mudraitā pañca varā proktā buddhaiścāpi maharddhikā ||",
    "679:305": "vajrapāṇirmahāpuṇyā tāṃ ca kṣipra suyojayet |",
    "679:306": "tathaiva hastāvudvartya śvetacandanakuṅkumaiḥ ||",
    "679:307": "tathaiva sampuṭākārau kuḍmalākāraveṣṭitau |",
    "679:308": "śiraḥsthāne tathā nyastau cāpi susthitau ||",
    "679:309": "sā tu vajraśirā jñeyā mahāmudrā hitā vidoḥ |",
    "679:310": "yakṣasenāpatermudrā dvitīyā bhavati mūrdhajā ||",
    "679:311": "uṣṇīṣamudrā hitā loke uṣṇīṣaṃ yakṣapaterhitam |",
    "679:312": "tadeva vajraṃ śirāmudrā ūrdhvamañjalisthāpitām ||",
    "679:313": "eṣa mudrā mahāmudrā uṣṇīṣeti pragīyate |",
    "679:314": "tṛtīyā vajrodbhavā nāma lalāṭasthāne tu sā bhavet ||",
    "679:315": "saṃnyastāñjalisampūrṇā dhruvau madhyeṣvanāmikau |",
    "679:316": "eṣā vajrodbhavā nāma vajrapāṇe'rthasādhikā ||",
    "679:317": "caturthī tu mahāmudrā vajravaktreti gīyate |",
    "679:318": "uttānau hastatalau nyasya veṇikākārasambhavau ||",
    "679:319": "vakṣaḥsthāne tathā nyasya madhyāṅgulyāṃ susūcitau |",
    "679:320": "eṣā mudrā mahāmudrā varā yakṣavare hitā ||",
    "679:321": "sarvavajrālayā ca sā |",
    "679:322": "pañca mātrā mahāmudrā vajrapāṇi maharddhikā ||",
    "679:323": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasya nābhisthāne tu kārayet |",
    "679:324": "tarjanyā kuñcitau kṛtvā aṅguṣṭhāgre tu nāmayet ||",
    "679:325": "tṛtīye parvamāśliṣya kanyasau ca susaṃsthitau |",
    "679:326": "baddhvo ca veṇikākārāṃ śeṣairaṅgulibhistadā ||",
    "679:327": "eṣā vajrālayā nāma mahāmudrā pragīyate |",
    "679:328": "atraiva sarvamudrā tu laukikā ye ca vajriṇe ||",
    "679:329": "śaivāḥ śakrakāścāpi riṣīṇāṃ ca maharddhikā hitā |",
    "679:330": "sā varā mataṅgino hyagrā mudrā proktā mahātmabhiḥ ||",
    "679:331": "yakṣarākṣasapretaiśca kūṣmāṇḍaiḥ kaṭaputanaiḥ |",
    "679:332": "ye tu mudrā varā proktā viṣṇvīndraiśca vanāhvayaiḥ ||",
    "679:333": "īśānamātarairlokagrahaiścāpi + + + + + + |",
    "679:334": "bhāskarenduvivasvākṣairvasavaścāpi supūjitaiḥ rakṣātmakaiḥ||",
    "679:335": "sṛṣṭā mudravarā ye tu sarvabhūtagaṇaiḥ sadā |",
    "679:336": "sarve caiva samāyānti mudre'smiṃ vajramālaye ||",
    "679:337": "prathitā mudravarā hyagrā kule'smiṃ vajramāhvaye |",
    "679:338": "muktā tathāgatīṃ mudrāṃ avalokīśasyāpi mahātmanaḥ |",
    "679:339": "mudrā hyeke te vai anyeṣāṃ prabhuriṣyate |",
    "679:340": "eṣā mudrā mahāmudrā yakṣasenāpatervidoḥ ||",
    "679:341": "yaṃ baddhvā puruṣā niyataṃ sarve bodhiparāyaṇāḥ |",
    "679:342": "eṣā mudrā varaḥ śreṣṭhaḥ paramāhustathāgatāḥ ||",
    "679:343": "hatyetā pañca mahāmudrā vajrapāṇe yaśasvinaḥ |",
    "679:344": "jāpibhiḥ sarvakālaṃ tu smartavyā ca mahābhaye ||",
    "679:345": "āśu naśyanti bhūtā vai kravyādā piśitāśinā |",
    "679:346": "yakṣarākṣasapretāṃsi kūṣmāṇḍāḥ kaṭapūtanā ||",
    "679:347": "devagandharvamanujāḥ kinnarāśca sasiddhakāḥ |",
    "679:348": "grahamukhyavarā garuḍā mātarāśca maharddhikāḥ ||",
    "679:349": "ye'pi te lokamukhyāśca brahmāviṣṇumaheśvarāḥ |",
    "679:350": "sarvasattvāśca vai loke yeṣu savartra māśṛtāḥ ||",
    "679:351": "sarve te dṛṣṭamātraṃ vai vidravanti na saṃśayaḥ |",
    "679:352": "ete mudrā jinaihyāsī vajradhṛte prabhoḥ ||",
    "679:353": "mantranāthasya yakṣeśe lokīśasyāpi mahātmane |",
    "679:354": "tasmācca jāpibhiḥ sarvaiḥ niyataṃ siddhilipsubhiḥ ||",
    "679:355": "smartavyā japakāle tu sarvamantreṣu siddhidā |",
    "679:356": "yo'sau kisalayetyāhuḥ mudrāmādau pragītavām ||",
    "679:357": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasya uraḥsthāne nyased budhaḥ |",
    "679:358": "tāmādau veṇikāṃ kṛtvā aṅgulībhiḥ samantataḥ ||",
    "679:359": "sā vidyā kisalaye mudrā laukikāṃ mantradevatām |",
    "679:360": "tāmādau yojayet kṣipraṃ kṣudrakarmeṣu dhīmatām ||",
    "679:361": "jvararogagatā sarvān nāśayennātra saṃśayaḥ |",
    "679:362": "saiva sumanasā jñeyā kanyasāṅgulināmitau ||",
    "679:363": "paṭahī tu bhavet sā tu madhyamāṅgulināmitau |",
    "679:364": "kandarpī ca bhavet sā ca ubhau aṅguṣṭhamucchritau ||",
    "679:365": "ghaṭakharparikā jñeyā anāmikāgrasunāmitau |",
    "679:366": "tathaiva kuḍmalaṃ kṛtvā hastāgrau ca subhūṣitau ||",
    "679:367": "utpalākāracihnaṃ tu mudramutpalamucyate |",
    "679:368": "vikāsitobhayau hastau aṅgulībhiḥ samantataḥ ||",
    "679:369": "eṣā vai padmamudrā tu bhave jyotsnā sanāmitau ||",
    "679:370": "tathaiva yojitāṃ sarvāṃ aṅgulyāgrāgrakāritā ||",
    "679:371": "eṣā suparṇine mudrā suparṇīti pragīyate |",
    "679:372": "tadeva lampuṭākāraṃ viparyastākāraceṣṭitam ||",
    "679:373": "sā bhaved yamalamudrā tu garutmasyāpi mahātmane |",
    "679:374": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasya muṣṭiyogena yojitau ||",
    "679:375": "ubhayāṅguṣṭhamadhyasthau liṅga mudreti gīyate |",
    "679:376": "utthitāṅguṣṭhamadhyasthau tadevaṃ śaṅkhamiṣyate ||",
    "679:377": "tadeva hastau visrajya jayā bhavati viśrutā |",
    "679:378": "vijayā bhavate mudrā kanyasāṅguliveṣṭitau ||",
    "679:379": "anāmikābhiḥ samāyuktā ajitā bhavati pūraṇī |",
    "679:380": "visṛjya hastau saṃyuktau vāmahastena mīlayet ||",
    "679:381": "aṅguṣṭhāgramadho nāmya muṣṭiṃ baddhveha paṇḍitaḥ |",
    "679:382": "eṣāparājitā jñeyā mudreyaṃ ca supūjitā ||",
    "679:383": "catuḥkumāryo vidhi jñeyā bhaginyeṣu prakīrtitā |",
    "679:384": "tumburustveṣa vikhyātaḥ jyeṣṭhabhrātā prakalpyate ||",
    "679:385": "nauyānasamāśritā hyete ambhodhestu nivāsinaḥ |",
    "679:386": "vicaranti imaṃ sthāne mahāpuṇyamaharddhikāḥ ||",
    "679:387": "vaśyārthaṃ sarvabhūtānāṃ sṛṣṭvā brahmavido vide |",
    "679:388": "sarvatra pūjitā hyetā guhyamantraistu yojitā ||",
    "679:389": "amoghā siddhimetāṃsi sarvakarmeṣu yojitā |",
    "679:390": "kṣipramarthakarāḥ siddhā maṅgalyā maghanāśanāḥ ||",
    "679:391": "śucinā śucikarmeṣu sādhanīyā tathottamaiḥ |",
    "679:392": "utthitaṃ jvalanaṃ śāntaṃ khacaraṃ kāyi siddhaye ||",
    "679:393": "madhyaṃ samadhyakarmeṣu aśaucaṃ kaśmalādiṣu |",
    "679:394": "ye cāpi pāpakarmā vai nityocchiṣṭāśca dehinām ||",
    "679:395": "teṣāṃ siddhyantyayatnena kṣudrakarmāṇi vai sadā |",
    "679:396": "tathaiva hastau saṃyamya nābhideśe samānayet ||",
    "679:397": "madhyamāṅgulyataḥ sūcyā veṇikākāra veṣṭayet |",
    "679:398": "sumekhalā ca sā mudrā udveṣṭā bhavati mekhalā ||",
    "679:399": "tameva madhatalau nyastau mudrā bhavati sampuṭā |",
    "679:400": "saivamucchritā grīve śrīsampuṭamucyate ||",
    "679:401": "nābhisthāne tadā nyasya apasavyena bhrāmayet |",
    "679:402": "rajanī mudravarā hyeṣā duṣṭasattvanivāraṇī ||",
    "679:403": "dakṣiṇe karamudyamya muṣṭiyogena māśrayet |",
    "679:404": "mudrāmuṣṭivaretyāhuḥ sarvamantrāṇi cūrṇanī ||",
    "679:405": "saivāṅgulimutsṛjya ubhau hastau prayojitā |",
    "679:406": "muṣṭimudrā varetyāhuḥ piśitāśananāśanī ||",
    "679:407": "sā tu saṅkucitā jñeyā aṅgulyāgrau sukuñcitau |",
    "679:408": "mudrā sukuntā vijñeyā kuntā caiva prasāritaiḥ ||",
    "679:409": "tārā sutārā vidhijñeyā ekarūpau ubhau bhavet |",
    "679:410": "utpalākārasaṃnyastā tarjanībhiḥ susaṃhatā ||",
    "679:411": "ekasūcikamityeva sampuṭākāraveṣṭitau |",
    "679:412": "tadeva prasāritā hastau tārā bhavati ghuṣyate ||",
    "679:413": "tadeva hastau saṃnyasya añjalyākārakāritau |",
    "679:414": "tarjanyā miśritau śreṣṭhau tṛtīye parvaṇi sthite ||",
    "679:415": "aṅguṣṭhau cānte mudrā bhavati locanā |",
    "679:416": "tadevāṅgulimutsṛjya tarjanyau samprayojitau ||",
    "679:417": "tadeva vihitā mudrā mudrā māmakyā samprayojitā |",
    "679:418": "evalā mudravaretyāhu madhyamāṅgulyaiḥ sunāmitaiḥ ||",
    "679:419": "śvetā yābhramudrā vai karaiścātra prasāritaiḥ |",
    "679:420": "paṇḍarā tu bhavenmudrā muṣṭibhiḥ samprapīḍitaiḥ ||",
    "679:421": "mahāprabhāvā mahāpuṇyā tarjanyāvucchritāvubhau |",
    "679:422": "tadeva hastau sammiśra sampuṭākāraveṣṭitau ||",
    "679:423": "tarjanībhiḥ tato kṛtvā netrākāraṃ tu pīḍayet |",
    "679:424": "bhrukuṭī mudravarā khyātā mahābhayaharī sadā ||",
    "679:425": "ityete cāṣṭa mudrā vai kathitā jinavaraiḥ purā |",
    "679:426": "mahāprabhāvā mahāpuṇyā maheśākhyā maharddhikā ||",
    "679:427": "sarvamudreṣu sarvatra mantraiścāpi viśeṣataḥ |",
    "679:428": "sarvatra pūjitā hyete smartavyārthaphalapradā ||",
    "679:429": "mahārakṣā pavitrāśca maṅgalyamaghanāśanāḥ |",
    "679:430": "sarvatra pūjitā buddhaiḥ sarvamantrāṃśca sādhayet ||",
    "679:431": "tārā bhṛkuṭī caiva śvetā paṇḍaravāsinī |",
    "679:432": "māmakī locanā caiva sutārā tāravartinī ||",
    "679:433": "ityete ca mahāmudrā paṭhitā lokatattvibhiḥ |",
    "679:434": "eṣa rakṣāvidhiḥ proktaḥ mahārakṣeṣu kathyate ||",
    "679:435": "mahāpāpaharī hyetā mahāmudrā svayambhuve |",
    "679:436": "lokīśasya ca vīrasya mahāyakṣapatestathā ||",
    "679:437": "ete mudrā mahāpuṇyā niyatā siddhihetavaḥ |",
    "679:438": "kathitā lokamukhyaiśca sambuddhaiśca yaśasvibhiḥ ||",
    "679:439": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasya vaiṇikākārasambhavau |",
    "679:440": "sampīḍitau viparyastau mudrā bhavati saṅkulā ||",
    "679:441": "tathaiva sūcikāgraṃ tu aṅkuśasyāhu varṇitaḥ |",
    "679:442": "tathaiva karapuṭo'graṃ vai unnanāmyo śiraḥsthitau ||",
    "679:443": "vikāsya aṅgulīṃ sarvāṃ chatrā bhavati śobhanā |",
    "679:444": "saṃyamya muṣṭikāmārau rātrī bhavati devatā ||",
    "679:445": "tāmasī visṛtairnityaṃ mudrā bhavati tattvataḥ |",
    "679:446": "tathaiva aṅgulāṃ veṣṭau ūrdhvamaṅguṣṭhanāmitau ||",
    "679:447": "viṣaninīśanā sṛṣṭā rekhamudrā yaśasvibhiḥ |",
    "679:448": "manasā nāmitau jñeyā mahāmānasamudritaiḥ ||",
    "679:449": "tathaiva hastāvutsṛjya ekahastena mīlayet |",
    "679:450": "tarjanyau veṣṭayenmadhyāṃ eṣā sā garuḍadhvajā ||",
    "679:451": "ubhau hastau samāyuktau veṇimāśṛtya madhyajau |",
    "679:452": "haṃsamāleti mudreyaṃ nāmnā sarvatra gīyate ||",
    "679:453": "tadeva visṛtau hastau tṛsūcyākāraveṣṭitau |",
    "679:454": "sā bhavet vajramudrā tu mudrā śreṣṭhatamā hitā ||",
    "679:455": "prakṛṣṭā sarvamudrāṇāṃ vajrapāṇeḥ samāhitā |",
    "679:456": "tadeva visṛtāṅgulyau padmamālā tu sā bhavet ||",
    "679:457": "jyeṣṭhā mudravarā khyātā padmaketoḥ samā bhavet |",
    "679:458": "eṣā mudravarā divyā mahāpuṇyā mahodbhavā ||",
    "679:459": "prayuktā sarvakarmeṣu siddhimāyānti dehinām |",
    "679:460": "bhuvi maṇḍalavikhyātā prasiddhā sarvakarmasu ||",
    "679:461": "vaktrārthavakritā jñeyā ubhau pāṇitale same |",
    "679:462": "sanyastāṅgulimagre tu tarjanyāṅgulimucchritā ||",
    "679:463": "mudrā vaktramiti jñeyā arddhavaktrā tu kanyasaiḥ |",
    "679:464": "samau muṣṭitalau jñeyau aṅguṣṭhottamanāmitau ||",
    "679:465": "lohitāmudramityāhuḥ madhyamānāmitasulohitā |",
    "679:466": "nīlalohitikā jñeyā mudrā rudrasya mūrdhnajā ||",
    "679:467": "mahāprabhāvā vikhyātā yā mudrā bhuvimaṇḍale |",
    "679:468": "sarvabighnaharī devī duṣṭasattvanivāraṇī ||",
    "679:469": "sā mudrā kathyate loke śṛṇudhvaṃ bhūtikāṃkṣiṇaḥ |",
    "679:470": "tathaiva hastau saṃyamya muṣṭimādau prakalpayet ||",
    "679:471": "visṛtau madhyamau jñeyau īṣit saṅkucitātha sūcitau |",
    "679:472": "mahāmudrā iti khyātā mudrā sā bhayasūdanī ||",
    "679:473": "tathaiva sūcyāgrau tau hastau suvyaktamīlitau |",
    "679:474": "eṣā viṣṇumiti khyātā mudrā sarvatra pūjitā ||",
    "679:475": "brāhmī tu bhave ubhau aṅguṣṭhamiśritau |",
    "679:476": "tathaiva kuḍmalākārā mudrā vaindrīti ucyate ||",
    "679:477": "sā bhavenmāheśvarī mudrā ubhau kanyasamucchritau |",
    "679:478": "tadeva hastāvutsṛjya nṛtyayogena māśrayet ||",
    "679:479": "vāmabāhustadā nityaṃ ubhayāgraṃ prakalpyate |",
    "679:480": "dakṣiṇaṃ bhujamāśliṣya tarjanyākāraveṣṭitam ||",
    "679:481": "eṣā vajradharā nityaṃ varāhīti prakalpyate |",
    "679:482": "tadeva visṛtau bāhū nṛtyayogena kalpitau ||",
    "679:483": "ubhau tarjanyākārataḥ kṣiprau vajracāmuṇḍi mucyate |",
    "679:484": "sa eva visṛtākārau ubhau pāṇau samāśṛtau ||",
    "679:485": "ūrdhvamāśṛtya gatā dṛṣṭiḥ ghorā cāmuṇḍi mucyate |",
    "679:486": "kaumārī tu bhavenmudrā kārttikeyasya mahāmahī ||",
    "679:487": "tadeva hastau vinyasya sūcyāgraṃ tu mīlayet |",
    "679:488": "visṛtairaṅgulībhiśca iyaṃ mudrā sarvamātarī ||",
    "679:489": "eṣā sarvamudrāṇāṃ mātarāṇāṃ tu maharddhikā |",
    "679:490": "etena sarvakarmā vai bāliśānāṃ tu kalpayetu ||",
    "679:491": "sūtikānāṃ ca nārīṇāṃ garbhasthānaṃ ca dehinām |",
    "679:492": "rakṣamokṣaṇamudreṣu pretavyantarakaśmalaiḥ ||",
    "679:493": "mokṣaṇārthaṃ tu kalpīta grahamātaranairṛtām |",
    "679:494": "hitārthaṃ prāṇināṃ loke mudrā bhavati sukhāvahā ||",
    "679:495": "śreyasaḥ sarvamantrāṇāṃ bhūtānāṃ prayuktā sukhadā hitā |",
    "679:496": "kṣudrakarmeṣu sarvatra yojayet sarvatra jāpinaḥ ||",
    "679:497": "ete mudrā sadā mantrairetaireva prayojayet |",
    "679:498": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasya svakuṇḍalābhogaveṣṭitau ||",
    "679:499": "aṅgulībhiḥ samantād vai mudrā nāgīti gīyate |",
    "679:500": "tathaiva maṅgulimadhyasthau sūcyāgraṃ tu mīlitau ||",
    "679:501": "bhavennāgamūkhī mudrā prakṛṣṭā sarvakarmasu |",
    "679:502": "yā sā mudravarā jñeyā mālā loke prakalpate ||",
    "679:503": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasya aṅgulībhiḥ samantataḥ |",
    "679:504": "veṇikākāra vaddhvā vai muṣṭyākāraṃ tu kārayet ||",
    "679:505": "tathaiva sampuṭākārau aṅguṣṭhau madhyanāmitau |",
    "679:506": "sā bhavenmālamudrā tu sarvakarmārthasādhanī ||",
    "679:507": "tathaiva maṅgulibhirnityaṃ ucchritaiḥ saptabhiḥ sadā |",
    "679:508": "sā tu saptacchadā mudrā tṛṣu lokeṣu gīyate ||",
    "679:509": "ete mudravarā hyagrā yathoktāste darśitā purā |",
    "679:510": "eteṣānāṃ tu mudrāṇāṃ nirdiṣṭā pūrvavistarām ||",
    "679:511": "sarvā hyekatamā jñeyā vidhinirdiṣṭadarśitā |",
    "679:512": "vistarārthagatā hyete vikalpārthāḥ savistarāḥ ||",
    "679:513": "smṛtāḥ sarve bhavenmudrā sarvamudraistu mudritā |",
    "679:514": "mudrā cāṣṭaśatā jñeyā uktā sarvārthasādhikā ||",
    "679:515": "eka eva bhavet teṣāṃ yathāsaṅkhyārthapūraṇī |",
    "679:516": "nṛtyayogena sthittvā vai ūrdhvaṃ paśyejjāpinaḥ ||",
    "679:517": "lalāṭa maṅgulī nyasya tarjanyā kanyasānvitām |",
    "679:518": "kṛtvā vai netrayogena sthitako'ñjalinā nyaset ||",
    "679:519": "sarvatrādarśanī nāma mudrā cāṣṭaśatātmikā |",
    "679:520": "anena mantrā sidhyante yathoktā sarvajñadarśinā ||",
    "679:521": "sarvamudrāstu atraiva prayoktavyā hyavikalpataḥ |",
    "679:522": "yathoktamudrāgaṇā hyeṣa ukto'yaṃ mantrasamāsata iti ||",
    "679:523": "āryamañjuśrīmūlakalpāt bodhisattvapiṭakāvataṃsakānmahāyānavaipulyasūtrāt sarvatathāgatācintyadharmadhātumudrāmudritā tricatvāriṃśatimaḥ svacaturtho mudrāpaṭalavisaraḥ |"
}